Construction source for the quotient-aware Theorem 3.11 multiradial package.

This removes three formerly raw payloads from the quotient-aware endpoint:
`multiradialImages` is constructed from the typed quotient and the record's
theta possible images; `selectedQRegion` is the possible image selected by
`selectedQChoice`; and the finite `F_l` cardinality is derived from `ZMod.card`.
The remaining explicit mathematical inputs are the image-invariance theorem for
